Class PaintTabs

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.control.Tab
com.example.paint.PaintTabs
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class PaintTabs extends javafx.scene.control.Tab
Malachinski Pain(t) Application - PaintTabs.java This class file is used to manage the changes made to individual tabs. This class also manages multiple canvases in the canvas stack, allowing for multiple canvases.
